    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 represents a superlative example of the E46 chassis. Powered by the S54B32 power plant, it features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering 333hp with surgical precision. The Getrag 6-speed manual ensures total mechanical engagement, while the M-variable differential lock provides peak corner-exit traction. This unit has received a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and VANOS bulletproofing to exceed factory durability. Rolling on forged Style 67 wheels with a factory-spec suspension geometry, it offers a pure, unadulterated driving experience. Mechanically flawless with zero leaks, no parasitic loss, and no deferred maintenance.",
