      "description": "This vehicle is a pristine example of automotive preservation, presenting in true showroom condition. The exterior features a flawless factory finish with a deep, mirror-like luster; there are no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections to be found. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the original alloy wheels are entirely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is immaculate and remains smoke-free, retaining its original scent. The premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, creasing, or fading, while the carpets and headliner are spotless. All technological features, including the navigation system and premium audio, operate as if brand new. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. It has been strictly garage-kept and never exposed to harsh weather conditions. This sale includes all original keys, the owner's manual, and a comprehensive folder of service records, offering complete peace of mind to the next owner.",
